title: So how much longer before i get the minion icon for the teemoing?
body: I got the all star and teemo icon already I but not the minion one yet. Is there someone who can look into this so to be sure I'm getting it eventually?

replies.body: Our aim is for the 17th per the [Teemoing ](http://na.leagueoflegends.com/en/featured/skins/the-teemoing-2016)page.  We're still sending out icons from the event, so hang tight.  The goodies will come.
